text: Zdeňka Padevětová (born 12 December 1958) is a retired archer from Czechoslovakia. She was born on 12 December 1958. Padevětová competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics.Zdeňka Padevětová == References == Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Czech archers Category:Olympians for the Czech Republic
